Modifications made for continuum v0.4
-------------------------------------
- @onlook/* workspace imports were localized:
    * @onlook/constants  -> inlined as ./constants.ts (only DATA_ONLOOK_ID etc.)
    * @onlook/utility    -> createOid/createDomId re-implemented in ./constants.ts
                            (nanoid customAlphabet, 3 lines) and customTwMerge
                            replaced with plain `twMerge` from `tailwind-merge`.
    * @onlook/models     -> not vendored; a tiny local CodeDiffRequest type is
                            defined in ./code-edit/transform.ts instead.
- code-edit/transform.ts was REDUCED to className + prop edits only. The
  structureChanges branch (group/insert/move/remove/image/text) and its module
  imports were dropped (out of scope for continuum v0.4 element editing).
- The Babel engine is `@babel/standalone` (same as upstream packages.ts).

Files in this directory and their upstream origin
-------------------------------------------------
  packages.ts            <- packages/parser/src/packages.ts            (verbatim)
  helpers.ts             <- packages/parser/src/helpers.ts             (verbatim)
